    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so incredibly excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such stunning shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept tucked away in a garage, and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone who appreciates a car that's been loved this much. If you're looking for something that's practically brand new, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
