    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. It has been treated with a high-end ceramic coating that makes the paint pop under any lighting. Inside, the cabin still retains that fresh factory scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of leather fatigue or bolster wear, and every tactile surface\u2014from the steering wheel to the switchgear\u2014feels brand new. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service performed exclusively at the authorized dealership, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. With remarkably low mileage and a comprehensive history file included, this car offers a genuine showroom-floor experience for the discerning enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
