    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46). This example features the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for optimal volumetric efficiency across the rev range. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with proactive rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and documented rear subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The chassis retains its factory-correct suspension geometry and original forged Style 67 wheels. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
